Has it ever occured to you that the activity within any speciality,
scientific or otherwise, is almost entirely dependent upon people, equipment
tools and understanding supplied by people whose speciality is different?

Has it also ever occured to you that the work done within any speciality
is almost enirely worthless unless it can be understood, appreciated and
utilised outside the speciality?



